*   [Oceanic ridge](/Oceanic_ridge): An underwater mountain system formed by plate tectonic spreading.
*   [Oceanic trench](/Oceanic_trench): Long, narrow, and incredibly deep depressions on the ocean floor.
*   [Outwash fan](/Outwash_fan): A fan-shaped deposit of sediment transported by meltwater from a glacier.
